wild_turkeys <- bird_counts %>% 
  filter(year >= 1955,
         species == "Wild Turkey")
wild_turkeys %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = year, y = how_many_counted)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  labs(title = "Raw data") 

model_lm <- lm(how_many_counted ~ year, data = wild_turkeys)
broom::augment(model_lm) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = year, y = .fitted)) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point()
